title: Nestor Cup Prologue
description: First race of the popular Nestor Cup Series. Bring out your roadie for a Merckx style time trial. Join us for one race or the entire series.
course: 2.1 mile time trial on the Hutchinson Island race track.
registration: Register online or on site day of the race. $15 preregistration, $20 day of race
notes: 1st- $35, 2nd- 25, 3rd- 20, 4th- 15, 5th- 10 Timing chip rental $5, may use own chip
directions: Follow I-16 East to Exit 166 (Gwinnett & Louisville Road, Charleston) go over Talmadge Bridge, Stay in right lane and turn right at base of the bridge onto Hutchinson Island, Follow signs to Trade & Convention Center, All parking is at the convention center. Turn right out of parking lot and left towards passed the golf club to the course.

title: Nestor Cup Race #1
description: Nestor Cup Series Race #1. The first crit of the year for the Cup. Race one or more races or race the entire 10 race series.
course: .8 mile loop on the Georgia Tech Savannah Campus
registration: Register online on the USAC site or day of the race. Riders must have a USA Cycling license. Category 5 men or category 4 women can purchase a USA Cycling one day license. All riders must sign a waiver. USA Cycling Rules apply
notes: Men's 4/5 30 minutes plus 3 laps, Men's 1/2/3/4/5 45+ 30 minutes plus 3 laps, Men's 1/2/3 45 minutes plus three laps, Women's 3/4 30 minutes plus 3 laps. 1st- $35, 2nd- 25, 3rd- 20, 4th- 15, 5th- 10 Timing chip rental $5, may use own chip
directions: I-95 to Exit 106 ( Jimmy Deloach Parkway), East on Jimmy Deloach, turn left into the Georgia Tech Savannah Campus

title: Nestor Cup Epilogue
description: A fun wrap up to the Nestor Cup Series. A 3 mile time trial to test your fitness just for fun. Compare your time at the end of the season to your time at the Prologue and see how your fitness has progressed. We will gather at B & D Burgers on Ellis Square after the event to re-cap all of the races from 2016.
course: 3 mile out and back time trial on the Hutchinson Island Speedway.
registration: Registration and chip rental is free. Please register online or day of event.
notes: All bike types are welcome. Start times are first come first off.
directions: Follow I-16 East to Exit 166 (Gwinnett & Louisville Road, Charleston) go over Talmadge Bridge, Stay in right lane and turn right at base of the bridge onto Hutchinson Island, Follow signs to Trade & Convention Center, All parking is at the convention center. Turn right out of parking lot and left towards passed the golf club to the course.
